{"id":232950869,"title":"九份老街阿妹茶樓","content":"晚上來九份又是另一種風格，尤其老街店家的燈火格外迷人，黃昏過後豎崎路旁的阿妹茶樓就是必遊的重點，當茶樓外的紅色燈籠跟黃色燈飾點起時，彷彿來到宮崎駿電影「神隱少女」中湯婆婆的湯屋。\n\n許多國外遊客也都知道這個熱門的拍攝景點，拍照當天傍晚時分燈一亮起阿妹茶樓前的豎崎路跟平臺就擠滿了觀光客，而且幾乎都是日韓遊客(女性居多)，近乎寸步難行，人手一機皆以阿妹茶樓為背景玩起合照或自拍，尖峰時段甚至找個位置架腳架都有困難。\n\n因此，Xavier建議傍晚想來阿妹茶樓跟豎崎路攝影的朋友，特別是假日務必提前抵達卡位做準備。阿妹茶樓對面又有一間有陽臺的茶樓，為這邊的最佳拍攝地點，但尖峰時段同樣一位難求、無法入內，得特別注意。\n\n\nhttp://i.imgur.com/2iQ8Hsy.jpg\n\nhttp://i.imgur.com/ltMaReY.jpg\n\nhttp://i.imgur.com/99bAgGi.jpg\n\nhttp://i.imgur.com/XtY7PS6.jpg\n\n完整介紹: https://peavy.pixnet.net/blog/post/47555247","excerpt":"晚上來九份又是另一種風格，尤其老街店家的燈火格外迷人，黃昏過後豎崎路旁的阿妹茶樓就是必遊的重點，當茶樓外的紅色燈籠跟黃色燈飾點起時，彷彿來到宮崎駿電影「神隱少女」中湯婆婆的湯屋。許多國外遊客也都知道這","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":false,"pinned":false,"forumId":"d0cd5819-4627-4b5f-8a8e-050976e0fba1","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-01-24T12:23:52.572Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-24T12:23:52.572Z","commentCount":3,"likeCount":12,"tags":[],"topics":["九份老街","單眼","攝影","相機","九份"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":true,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"攝影","forumAlias":"photography","school":"Xavier","department":"sanchers","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":12}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"http://i.imgur.com/2iQ8Hsy.jpg"},{"url":"http://i.imgur.com/ltMaReY.jpg"},{"url":"http://i.imgur.com/99bAgGi.jpg"},{"url":"http://i.imgur.com/XtY7PS6.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"d65eb92e-c8ef-47d0-a72a-5c634bf7398a","url":"https://i.imgur.com/2iQ8Hsyl.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/2iQ8Hsyl.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/2iQ8Hsyl.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2020-01-24T12:23:52.572Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-24T12:23:52.572Z"},{"id":"d65eb92e-c8ef-47d0-a72a-5c634bf7398a","url":"http://i.imgur.com/2iQ8Hsy.jpg